  "detailed_description": "<strong>Extreme Peg Solitaire</strong> is a minimalist game designed for Peg Solitaire and puzzle lovers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play through 60 hand designed puzzles.<br></li><li>Play with different unique pegs.<br></li><li>Collect stars to master the game<br></li><li>Enjoy the classic mode and play the regular Peg Solitaire.<br></li><li>Choose the background sound for your puzzle.<br></li><li>Play with the mouse, keyboard or gamepad.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574690/extras/a36cffcc8e2ba40ccdeeee24b42bb4d6.webp?t=1618023110\" width=591 height=34 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574690/extras/3e94ea807cb66710c79821852327d180.poster.avif?t=1618023110\" width=591 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574690/extras/3e94ea807cb66710c79821852327d180.webm?t=1618023110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Jump over another ghost.<br></li><li>Only one ghost can survive.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574690/extras/78e1c2c43db78710dc94347c7ae2b989.webp?t=1618023110\" width=591 height=34 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574690/extras/6464d3b43a6b314703bd7b871c950c17.poster.avif?t=1618023110\" width=591 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574690/extras/6464d3b43a6b314703bd7b871c950c17.webm?t=1618023110\" type=\"video/we